## Invite a Specific Employee

```shell
curl -X PATCH "<%= config[:base_url] %>/employees/<ID>/invite" \\
     -H 'x-api-key: <%= config[:api_key] %>' \\
     -H 'tio-auth-token: <%= config[:api_token] %>' \\
```

This endpoint sends an invite to an eligible employee.

<aside class="warning">
Invite emails are automatically sent after creating a new employee.
This endpoint will <b>re-send</b> a new invite if the specified employee has not yet registered with Tuition.io.
</aside>

### HTTP Request

`PATCH <%= config[:base_url]%>/employees/<ID>/invite`

### URL Parameters

Parameter | Description
--------- | -----------
ID | The ID of the employee to invite
